title: Clint Black ends a 10-year drought of new music with 'On Purpose' (CD review)
text:
Clint Black ends a 10-year drought of new music with 'On Purpose' (CD review) 
Published By: Cleveland.com - Today 
Clint Black is back with his first new studio album in 10 years, "On Purpose'' and it puts his expressive voice on full display....
